sentences.sentence: Based on in-depth analysis of the"identity", we found that the"identity"is intensional.
sentences.translation: 通过对“同一”的深入分析，发现“同一”是内涵性的，即传递了符号之间的语形或语义联系。

sentences.sentence: When an intensional node-set is used for the third time, it is stored extensionally, trading memory for processing time.
sentences.translation: 当第三次使用内包节点集时，将在扩展存储它，以内存换取处理时间。

sentences.sentence: An intensional shaking may be the most well-known sign of Parkinson's, but it can also calls stiffness or slower movements.
sentences.translation: 一次频繁的震动可能是最知名的帕金森氏症的迹象，但它也可以是僵硬或较慢的动作。
